title: [PS3] Rust Buccaneers
description:
<a href="http://www.rustbuccaneers.com/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://www.rustbuccaneers.com/</a>

Rust Buccaneers is an arcade ship shooter game with an immense 36 unique player ship selection. Filled with action, explosions, cool weapons and tactical game play makes Rust Buccaneers the most appealing short session game this year. The player gets rewarded with new interesting ships when playing. The boat selection varies from the small water jet to the massive aircraft carrier, in which you can actually control the aircrafts leaving the ship and strike your enemies with machine guns and bombs. You can complete the game in single player mode or with a friend in co-op. You can also battle against friends in versus mode and the computer in versus AI mode.
